#################################################################

###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#metamodelingPolicy
<http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox#metamodelingPolicy> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty ;
                                                             rdfs:comment "Documents ontology-wide expectations for explicit punning-based typing of classes and individuals"@en ;
                                                             rdfs:label "Metamodeling policy"@en ;
                                                             <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guideline> .


###  http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment
